{"tid":1479820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人講今日黃埔路線!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T06:34:27.000Z","uid":209041,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b66e34e6e5e2c3d193fa41c777a01215858da8f6","tid":1479820,"uid":209041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n黃埔友見無乜人講路線<br />\n都有啲擔心<br />\n所以同家父略略整咗嗰地圖<br />\n希望大家出發前都大概知黃埔嘅地勢<br />\n有錯請指正<br />\n坦白講 黃埔雖然冇元朗咁複雜<br />\n但嗰地勢都幾仆街<br />\n首先比大家睇黃埔終點站嘅地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcXv99w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcXv99w.png&h=c17ef6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA同B出口都有天橋可以走<br />\n呢區總共有10條天橋 <br />\n(Google map:綠色人仔pin;圖:藍色highlight)<br />\n可以通往其他cite<br />\n不過一定要注意嘅係<br />\n黃埔花園始終係私人地方<br />\n而且呢區全部都有cctv<br />\n所以自己睇路<br />\n另外黃埔呢區太多秘道/樓梯<br />\n有時真係冇為意 但咁其實好危險<br />\n最明顯亦有標記到嘅就係戴亞街嘅警署<br />\n(Google map:紅色pin;圖:黃色骷髏骨頭)<br />\n兩邊有樓梯落 再後啲108商場都有樓梯<br />\n佢地隨時衝落嚟殺我地個措手不及<br />\n點解我話嗰地勢好仆街 睇呢張相就知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69SDzBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69SDzBs.jpg&h=98e2162f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綠色箭嘴：(大)紅磡狗屋可經佛光街落嚟 <br />\n藍色箭嘴：(中)西九交通狗屋，可以經街市個邊入嚟 <br />\n紅色交叉: 上次已經試過放幾架狗車 防暴可以經三條樓梯落 車就可以係大環山同兜去德民街到包抄<br />\n橙色箭嘴：(細)水狗屋，可以經大環山個邊入嚟<br />\n黃色箭嘴：尖沙咀狗可以經火車站個邊backup<br />\n基本上係等比人包抄<br />\n而唯一安全退路就係map pin咗黃色星星呢到<br />\n圖入面亦都有綠色公仔講行嘅方向<br />\n上咗橋過對面海濱一直沿住條橋行<br />\n一路上就係海韻軒同都會海逸酒店<br />\n嗰到無乜cam同小啲人<br />\n又近酒店 可以換裝後走去紅磡火車站/尖東/poly<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdA5Y3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdA5Y3r.jpg&h=13a2d099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預咗全黃埔商場都可能封<br />\nAeon講咗9點收 但唔排除會再早啲收<br />\n大家萬事小心 希望可以見到大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd92e09cd63d092bb68b62cdc5be9ff5490c5bad","tid":1479820,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9044983cea38e4aacfee2beca3baade794db7e41","tid":1479820,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UepRUDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUepRUDi.jpg&h=f2b539e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e7308d2b75d6176492f8d3f749efa6cb62d0f58","tid":1479820,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd3205694683eb0d444d8e56779582e3f194f5be","tid":1479820,"uid":209041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"自推10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f253216913632c79cd7162fdc997c0e063ab24e2","tid":1479820,"uid":225985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b62129e1c400d76793a2cba0c440886283b7c73","tid":1479820,"uid":241979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"落去圍埋黃埔圍埋新城間垃圾中立電台得唔得？"},{"pid":"1c9c4b20d5782d283cdebd1fee835e23cff323ef","tid":1479820,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"call 定啲poly人去接仔"},{"pid":"9b1103cc94a9b8c8320a804bd807015b8d7d14cd","tid":1479820,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d55f087dea488dcd2d0b7e53553d8c6ad626d93","tid":1479820,"uid":136137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"817"},{"pid":"e4d1605af65018ab693526fc3f0b62d55b7abf36","t